OL,5, Four out of every 10 police forces in  
OL,6, England and Wales are failing to ask   
OL,7, arrested suspects whether they have a  
OL,8, gambling addiction, data reveals.      
OL,10,FScreening for drug or alcohol addiction
OL,11,Fand mental-health problems is standard 
OL,12,Fpractice among police forces.          
OL,14,FBut 41% of forces fail to include      
OL,15,Fgambling, a Freedom of Information     
OL,16,Frequest shared exclusively with BBC    
OL,17,FRadio 4's File on 4 programme reveals. 
OL,19,FThe National Police Chiefs Council said
OL,20,Fit was working to improve screening.   
